title: Time for Turnbull govt to abandon unpopular environmental law change (Greenpeace Australia Pacific)
text: ( Source : Greenpeace Australia Pacific ) Sydney , 13 October 2015 - The government knows it is on shaky ground over attempts to weaken Australia's environmental protection law and should just abandon the effort completely, Greenpeace Australia
